snippet.title: Duels of Fortune: Steam Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
!!! DUELS OF FORTUNE IS CURRENTLY IN EARLY ACCESS. ALL GAMEPLAY, SOUNDS, AND VISUALS ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE !!!

Duels of Fortune is coming to Steam Early Access very soon!

For the occasion, we've essentially recreated our EVO trailer from last year, but included some of the extra content and characters that have added since then!

All music created By Kyle Keller of Jack7 Productions (https://soundcloud.com/jack7music-1 & https://jack7.itch.io/) except where specifically noted.

Download Duels of Fortune for free here!
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2371130/Duels_of_Fortune/
Itch - https://cosmic-hat-games.itch.io/duels-of-fortune

Follow us on Twitter! - https://twitter.com/CosmicHatGames
Join the Discord community! - https://discord.gg/R5vVYyR
